title: Regular curve

A //regular curve// is a [[differentiable|Ableitung]] [[curve|Kurve]] $$\gamma\colon\R\supset I\to\R^n$$ with $$\gamma'(t)\ne 0$$ for all $$t\in I.$$ Let

$$
T(t)\coloneqq\frac 1 {|\gamma'(t)|} \gamma(t),
\qquad N(t)\coloneqq\begin{pmatrix} 0 &-1 \\ 1 &0\end{pmatrix} T(t)
$$

denote the unit tangent vector field and unit normal vector field of $$\gamma.$$